  "title": "safety coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Job Description & Requirements</p><ul><li>Site coordination with project site-in-charge.</li><li>Provides specific support for monitoring injury, illness, and incident related performance.</li><li>Examines permits, licenses, applications, and records to ensure compliance with HSE requirements.</li><li>Prepare, organize, and maintain inspection records.</li><li>Investigates complaints and suspected violations.</li><li>Monitors follow-up actions in cases where violations were found, and reviews compliance monitoring reports.</li><li>Supports the specific HSE plans, playbooks, and procedures as assigned by manager/supervisor.</li><li>Submit PTW, method statement, tool box and permit application.</li><li>Report on accidents and participate in risk assessments.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties assigned.</li></ul>",
