    "description": "<p>VINA Specialist Pte Ltd is a leader in providing our clients with a wide range of Rope Access services and solutions. We have full-time rope workforce and have the best track records in providing quality rope access services.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our Rope Access Technicians are IRATA (Industrial Rope Access Trade Association) trained and certified and have undergone specialized training in different aspects. We provide a comprehensive range of services, which consists of Industrial, Commercial, Residential, Engineering, Lightning Protection System (LPS), Heat Shielding, Bird Management, Wind Turbines, CompEX and Rental &amp; Sales. VINA specializes in integrated services with end-to-end access solutions for Marine Offshore, Oil &amp; Gas, Civil Construction and Structural Maintenance Industries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>VINA has recently explored into a new business venture – Solar Management for Industrial / Commercial / Residential.</p>",
